hu.mta.sztaki.lpds.cloud.simulator.energy.powermodelling
Interface PowerState.PowerCharacteristicsChange

All Known Implementing Classes:
DirectEnergyMeter
Enclosing class:
PowerState
public static interface PowerState.PowerCharacteristicsChange

allows notifications before the consumption characteristics would change. Useful to update instantaneous power draw values before a power characteristic change (like going from turboboost->using all cpu cores in modern processors)

Author:
"Gabor Kecskemeti, Laboratory of Parallel and Distributed Systems, MTA SZTAKI (c) 2014"
